content:
Reopen a completed swarm from Lightning Experience to seamlessly restart the conversation. Reopening a swarm changes it from a Closed status to an Open one. 

From the record in Salesforce, select Reopen Swarm.
Choose how you want to reopen the swarm, and then click Next.
Verify that the swarm was reopened, and then select Finish
title: Reopening a Swarm in Salesforce Service Cloud
